.SH INPUT FORMATS
The following input formats are accepted:
.IP \(bu 2
Unix epoch in seconds (1\-10 digits) or milliseconds (11\-13 digits),
auto\-detected by digit count.
Negative epochs (pre\-1970) are accepted, e.g.\ \f[B]\-86400\f[R].
.IP \(bu 2
